{"tid":2161341,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"港台有節目講香港野牛同牛義工","createTime":"2020-08-17T13:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T12:55:27.000Z","uid":41818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ca676f9f20240a75dfbeec43ce6869b2f0c6f8eb","tid":2161341,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:24:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XP17s2_oGqg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXP17s2_oGqg&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21NagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=60ddaef5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XP17s2_oGqg</a><br />\n<br />\n自古以來，牛都是農夫工作的伙伴。然而，隨着城市發展，人們不再需要牛去耕田，但牛依然生活在鄉郊地區。人和牛如何在同一片天空下和平共存呢？<br />\n<br />\n有牧牛人無懼風雨，天天與牛同行，嘗試為牛羣爭取一片自在呼吸的天地；有義工出錢出力，經常割草、送草給牛羣，希望使牠們免受饑餓之苦。這份愛牛的善心又如何傳遞下去呢？"},{"pid":"d6dad489f18b53e215aef9e55c7b4cb169a65aa4","tid":2161341,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f2e18ff012a61a4cf478e05e34e2d5d26387e0","tid":2161341,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:55:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}